---
title: Cheesy Smokehouse Bean Jacket Potatoes with Plant-Based Mayo & Cucumber Salad
description: Saddle up for a taste of the great outdoors with this cheesy plant-based delight! These spuds are stuffed to the brim with hearty cannellini beans and pops of sweetcorn, perfect for huddling around a warm campfire. Served with a crunchy cucumber salad and creamy plant-based mayo, you can’t go wrong.

